@startuml
title Mapper Stage - State Machine Diagram (Current)
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #e8f1fb
  BorderColor #b9d2ec
}

[*] --> Input

Input --> UpstreamBlocked : collected.errors exists
Input --> Mapping : valid collected record

Mapping --> RuleEval
RuleEval --> RuleEval : next rule
RuleEval --> SchemaCheck : all rules processed

SchemaCheck --> SinkCheck
SinkCheck --> MetaRules : no hard errors
SinkCheck --> Failed : hard errors

MetaRules --> Mapped
Failed --> Output
Mapped --> Output
UpstreamBlocked --> Output

Output --> [*]

note right of SinkCheck
Sink shape validation is warning-level\nfor MAP (non-fatal by design).
end note

@enduml
